creator: upjers GmbH
descriptionHtml:
My Free Farm 2 – Create your own Farm!

Experience the colorful world of My Free Farm 2. Cultivate your fields, keep and care for cuddly animals and process your farm fresh produce into all kinds of wonderful hand-crafted products. The possibilities are limitless! Let yourself be enchanted by this extraordinary farm game and discover My Free Farm 2!

Fantastic Farm Game Opportunities!

My Free Farm offers you an impressive 3D farm setting. Decorate your farm with beautiful decorations, build all kinds of production buildings, make virtual friends with your fellow players and dive into a lovingly detailed world. Zoom in close to admire the stunning details on your plants and animal and explore every corner of your farm property. Make use of countless farm game features:

• Grow dozens of crops
• Keep and care for adorable animals
• Manufacture fabulous farm goods
• Expansive story quests
• Countless expansions and many unique decorations for your farm
• Regular farm game updates and events
• Intuitive game controls

My Free Farm 2 – Countryside Idyll on the Go!

Let the farm game fun can begin! Download My Free Farm 2 for your device and get your own mobile farm now. Come check out the fantastic farm game. Tend to your fields, expand your farm, care for cuddly critters, and make your farm prosper!

A Captivating Gaming Experience

Fresh air, beautiful country scenery, infinite possibilities and exciting challenges – My Free Farm 2 is a farm game destined to provide long-lasting farming fun! Try it out now – get the app and run your own farm!
descriptionShort: My Free Farm 2 - Design your own Farm in 3D with Cute Animals!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: The handyman gang has visited My Free Farm 2 and fixed a few things here and there - squeaking doors have been oiled, cracks in the walls have been filled - in a word: bugfixes!

This new update will please your taste buds! But first we’re celebrating the game’s 9th anniversary with you. Soon we’ll add some spices to your 3D farm life with many condiments as new products. You are in for an Italian treat later this year when we will launch a fantastic new product line-up: olives and pasta are just two of the savory novelties. Get this update – the probably yummiest of them all!

creator: upjers GmbH
descriptionHtml:
My Free Farm 2 - Create Your Farm!

Experience the vibrant farm game of My Free Farm 2. Cultivate fields, care for cute animals, process harvests into agricultural products, and design a farm according to your vision! Discover the enchanting world of this exceptional farm game.

Exciting features:

🌾 Grow various plants
🐷 Care for adorable animals
🏡 Produce farm goods in buildings
👩‍🌾 Engage in customer quests
🌼 Expand and decorate your farm
🌿 Regular updates and events
🌻 User-friendly controls

Get the mobile farm experience with My Free Farm 2. Download the game for free and explore the immersive farm gameplay. Cultivate fields, expand your farm, care for animals, and build your dream farm.

My Free Farm 2 - Farming on the go!
descriptionShort: My Free Farm 2 - Design your own Farm in 3D with Cute Animals!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: It’s getting Christmassy in My Free Farm 2 First of all, you are going to get new hot beverages for winter season. Enjoy fruit punch with apple, orange or cherry flavor. Next you’ll get a new building – the interior decorator. Produce desks, cribs and all types of shelves from wood. That will be the perfect furniture for “elf on a shelf” to ring in Christmas Season! This year you’re in for another beautiful Christmas Event, an Advent Calendar and many presents more. Get the update now!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Extra long birthday party for 10th anniversary. We are celebrating 10 years of My Free Farm 2 fun with three events in a row! Earn three fantastic farm decorations between May 13 and June 3 for your farm! We also hired the production administrator for your farm. Check out the brand-new feature offering you a fantastic overview over all of your buildings. It allows you to pick up produced goods and to start new productions. Enjoy the production administrator during the first three days for free!
